  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IN 2024: You are a detective who went to investigate a case at a shop. Find clues and search where are Mary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an investigation game where instead of you following a detective investigating, you are the detective, the game makes absolutely NOTHING clear and you as a detective need to understand what is happening by investigating the scenarios and drawing your own conclusions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FLASHLIGHT:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your flashlight to view hidden things!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017570/extras/3c6b02a42f6aab58b9de8c839372643c.avif?t=1772382056\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017570/extras_big/3c6b02a42f6aab58b9de8c839372643c.avif?t=1772382056 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CAMERA:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use camera mode to view small things!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017570/extras/325f2d26fa0126be064413292350b733.avif?t=1772382056\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017570/extras_big/325f2d26fa0126be064413292350b733.avif?t=1772382056 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEDUCT:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What is happening?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017570/extras/31b5fa96f6d86e30baff56e121375568.avif?t=1772382056\" width=300 height=154 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IN 2024: You are a detective who went to investigate a case at a shop. Find clues and search where are Mary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an investigation game where instead of you following a detective investigating, you are the detective, the game makes absolutely NOTHING clear and you as a detective need to understand what is happening by investigating the scenarios and drawing your own conclusions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FLASHLIGHT:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your flashlight to view hidden things!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017570/extras/3c6b02a42f6aab58b9de8c839372643c.avif?t=1772382056\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017570/extras_big/3c6b02a42f6aab58b9de8c839372643c.avif?t=1772382056 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CAMERA:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use camera mode to view small things!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017570/extras/325f2d26fa0126be064413292350b733.avif?t=1772382056\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017570/extras_big/325f2d26fa0126be064413292350b733.avif?t=1772382056 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEDUCT:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What is happening?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017570/extras/31b5fa96f6d86e30baff56e121375568.avif?t=1772382056\" width=300 height=154 /></span></p>",
